Package: metero
Title: Meta-analysis Tool for Exploring Antimicrobial Resistance Outcomes
    Across Realms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chaokun", "Hong", , "chaokun.hong@ndm.ox.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive tool for analysis and visualization of
    antimicrobial resistance (AMR) meta-analysis data. The package
    implements the One Health approach, integrating human, animal, and
    environmental AMR data. It provides functions for data import,
    standardization, meta-analysis, trend analysis, and interactive
    visualization of AMR patterns across different pathogens, antibiotics,
    geographic regions, and domains.
